title: The Cats - Collection of 8 albums [160Kbps]
description:
This is a collection of 8 albums from the Dutch 60s palingpop group "The Cats". 
Palingpop refers to the place they were from: Volendam, a fishermen&#039;s village (paling means eel) on the westcoast of the IJsselmeer that has produced a proportionately high number (perhaps the highest number in the Netherlands) of both musicians and soccer players.

This is not a complete collection, by far, but there seems to be no other torrent available on the net.
